IMAPAccount gmail-work
Host imap.gmail.com
User magautie@redhat.com
PassCmd "oauth2get gmail redhat"
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs XOAUTH2

IMAPStore gmail-work
Account gmail-work

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/redhat
Inbox ~/Mail/redhat

Channel redhat
Far :gmail-work:
Near :gmail-local:
# Automatically create missing mailboxes on server only
Create Far
Patterns INBOX archive
## Save the synchronization state files in the relevant directory
SyncState *

#Channel gmail-special-folders
#Far ":gmail-work:[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
#Near :gmail-local:sent
#Create Near
#SyncState *

